title: Soft Golden Hour
description: Coastal overlook at golden hour with warm lighting and nostalgic atmosphere
searchTerms: coastal overlook at golden hour with warm lighting
prompt: A quiet coastal overlook at golden hour. Low-angle warm sunlight paints a couple leaning on a railing as elongated soft-edged shadows trail behind them. Warm rim separation outlines their faces with a honeyed glow, gentle falloff keeps contrast soft, and slightly lifted blacks give a nostalgic warmth. White balance sits around ~4500K as they trade calm smiles and watch waves roll in.
